"id":"rec9d3hvIavLm4Svw","ref":"Mark.8.3","text":"And if I send them away fasting to their own houses, they will faint by the way: for divers of them came from far.","year":32},{"id":"rectVKE2mHE09Ylxv","ref":"Mark.8.4","text":"And his disciples answered him, From whence can a man satisfy these men with bread here in the wilderness?","year":32},{"id":"recVu2yhCcnzoBC4K","ref":"Mark.8.5","text":"And he asked them, How many loaves have ye? And they said, Seven.","year":32},{"id":"recZQdg5tKrpBIEXr","ref":"Mark.8.6","text":"And he commanded the people to sit down on the ground: and he took the seven loaves, and gave thanks, and brake, and gave to his disciples to set before them; and they did set them before the people.","year":32},{"id":"rec396aCQ0aboXhNE","ref":"Mark.8.7","text":"And they had a few small fishes: and he blessed, and commanded to set them also before them.","year":32},{"id":"recVHbVcSZOu7tMor","ref":"Mark.8.8","text":"So they did eat, and were filled: and they took up of the broken meat that was left seven baskets.","year":32}]}
